00010 /* Purpose: Provides routines necessary for converting the   */
00011 /*   the LHS of a rule into an appropriate form suitable for */
00012 /*   the KB Rete topology. This includes transforming the    */
00013 /*   LHS so there is at most one "or" CE (and this is the    */
00014 /*   first CE of the LHS if it is used), adding initial      */
00015 /*   patterns to the LHS (if no LHS is specified or a "test" */
00016 /*   or "not" CE is the first pattern within an "and" CE),   */
00017 /*   removing redundant CEs, and determining appropriate     */
00018 /*   information on nesting for implementing joins from the  */
00019 /*   right.                                                  */
